A Fat Boy who was insecure about his weight was forced by his family to go to the Stadium for running , in order to lose some weight . He saw many Athletes practising in the stadium in their respective games . Highly influenced by them , he decided to build his career in field of sports . He started participating in every game to check his potential and to check which game he actually belongs to . Once he tried javelin throw and threw it way farther than any athelete in that stadium could , everyone was stunned . That Kid is none other than our Gold Medalist Neeraj Chopra . What a Story !
